title: Dakine Frankie Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Frankie Pack in our Sierra print.
Pack Features:
- Side access fleece lined padded laptop compartment
- Fits most 15" laptops
- Interior padded fleece lined sleeve for iPad
- Breathable DriMesh® back panel and shoulder straps
- Back panel security pocket
- Document pocket
- Organizer pocket
- Water bottle pocket
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Padded bottom panel
